snippet.title: Thymesia | 18 mins of new Gameplay [4K UHD 60FPS]
snippet.description:
(PC) Thymesia - Gameplay Walkthrough Full Demo | No Commentary [4K UHD 60FPS]

This is the full demo for Thymesia on Steam. The demo can be beaten in 10 minutes if you are super skilled. Took me about 45 mins. Enemies require patience and learning. Especially the elites. Enjoy!
